val.&lt;wbr&gt;com/a/Siva_&lt;wbr&gt;Shiva/id/&lt;wbr&gt;137936&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;u&gt;Siva, Shiva (Sans=
krit) The third god of the Hindu Trimurti (trinity)&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;br&gt;
Brahma the evo=
lver; Vishnu the preserver; and Siva the regenerator or&lt;br&gt;
