form, whose fierce passions make of him the &#39;roarer,&#39; =
the &#39;terrible&#39; &quot;&lt;br&gt;
(SD 2:613, 548).&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Siva is often spoken of=
 as the patron deity of esotericists,&lt;br&gt;
occultists, and ascetics; he is c=
alled the Mahayogin (the great&lt;br&gt;
